Business Term(s): English Name, Foreign Name, Also Known As Name, Trade Alias Name

DEN: Procuring_ Organization. Primary. Tendering_ Contact
Definition: The primary contact information for this procuring organization in the tendering process.

DEN: Procuring_ Organization. Alternate_ Designated. Tendering_ Contact
Definition: Information for an alternate designated contact within this procuring organization.

DEN: Procuring_ Organization. Postal. Tendering_ Address
Definition: The postal address for this procuring organization in the tendering process.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Details
Definition: An endeavour carefully planned to achieve a procurement of goods, works and service.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier of this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Description. Text
Definition: The textual description of this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Name. Text
Definition: The name, expressed as text, of this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Works Type. Code
Definition: A code specifying the type of work, such as surveying or consulting, for this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Sub_ Works Type. Code
Definition: A code specifying the type of sub works, such as land surveying or information technology consulting, for this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Type. Code
Definition: The code specifying the type of procuring project, such as goods, works and service.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Constraint. Indicator
Definition: The indication of whether or not the project is constrained by an authority such as the World Trade Organization (WTO) for this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Total_ Budget. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the total budget which includes net amount, taxes, and material and instalment costs for this procuring project.
Publication comments: It includes all expenses, for example, the construction amount, tax and instalment costs for the supplier’s service as well as material costs paid by the owner institution, because construction materials can be ordered separately from the construction service itself.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Net_ Budget. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the net budget for this procuring project.
Publication comments: This excludes tax, the costs of installing equipment, and material costs from the total size of budget.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Physical. Project Actualization_ Location
Definition: The physical actualization location of this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Plan. Tendering_ Period
Definition: The planned period for performing this procuring project in the tendering process.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Specified. Inspection_ Event
Definition: The inspection event specified for this procuring project.

DEN: Procuring_ Project. Plan. Project_ Period
Definition: A planned period for this procuring project.

DEN: Produce_ Batch. Details
Definition: A group of produce dealt with together.

DEN: Produce_ Batch. Collector Assigned_ Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier for this produce batch assigned by a collector.

DEN: Produce_ Batch. Farmer Assigned_ Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier for this produce batch assigned by a farmer.

DEN: Produce_ Batch. Weight. Measure
Definition: The measure of the weight (mass) of this produce batch.

DEN: Produce_ Batch. Applicable. Technical_ Characteristic
Definition: A technical characteristic applicable to this produce batch.

DEN: Product Characteristic_ Condition. Details
Definition: A state that applies to a product characteristic.

Definition: The code specifying the type of product characteristic condition.

DEN: Product Characteristic_ Condition. Name. Text
Definition: A name, expressed as text, for this product characteristic condition.

DEN: Product Characteristic_ Condition. Value. Measure
Definition: The measure of the value for this product characteristic condition.

DEN: Product Component_ Itinerary. Product End. Time

Definition: The specified area, expressed as text, for this product component itinerary.

DEN: Product Component_ Itinerary. Included. Lodging House_ Travel Product Sub-Component
Definition: The lodging house travel product sub-component included in this product component itinerary.

DEN: Product Information_ Contact. Details
Definition: A person or department that acts as a point of contact for product information.

Definition: A code specifying a type of product information contact.

DEN: Product Information_ Contact. Telephone. Telecommunication_ Communication

DEN: Product Information_ Contact. Fax. Telecommunication_ Communication
Definition: The fax telecommunication for this product information contact.

DEN: Product Information_ Contact. URI. Internet_ Communication
Definition: The internet communication of the URI for this product information contact.

DEN: Production_ Software. Details
Definition: A software program or software used in a production process, such as supporting information inputs and outputs.

Definition: The unique identifier of the version of this production software.

Definition: The code specifying the product availability status.

Definition: The number of product units available for sale.

DEN: Product_ Availability. Description. Text
Definition: The textual description of this product availability.

DEN: Product_ Availability. Applicable. Available_ Period
Definition: An available period applicable to this product availability.

DEN: Product_ Batch. Details
Definition: A group of products considered or dealt with together.

Definition: The identifier for this product batch.

Definition: The weight, expressed as a measure, for this product batch.

Definition: A treatment, expressed as text, applied to this product batch.

Definition: An agricultural certificate specified for this product batch.

DEN: Product_ Batch. Specified. Agricultural Input_ Product
Definition: An agricultural input product specified for this product batch.

DEN: Product_ Batch. Applied. Specified_ Agricultural Application
Definition: A specified agricultural application applied to this product batch.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Details
Definition: A collection of data for a piece of written, printed or electronic matter that provides information or evidence about the product.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Identification. Identifier
Definition: The identifier for this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Issue. Date Time
Definition: The date, time, date time, or other date time value when this product certificate was issued.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Expiry. Date Time
Definition: The date, time, date time, or other date time value when this product certificate expires.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Issue Reason. Code
Definition: The code specifying the reason why this product certificate was issued.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Type. Code
Definition: A code specifying the type of product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Requested Effective. Date Time
Definition: The requested effective date, time, date time or other date time value for this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Actual Effective. Date Time
Definition: The actual effective date, time, date time or other date time value for this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Description. Text
Definition: A textual description of this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Applicable_ Object. Code
Definition: A code specifying an object, such as item, animal, person or organization applicable for this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Issuing_ Party. Identifier
Definition: The identifier for the party issuing this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Certificate. Purpose. Code
Definition: A code specifying the purpose of this product certificate.

DEN: Product_ Security Tag. Details
Definition: A product tag device to provide protection from a peril such as theft.

DEN: Product_ Security Tag. Type. Code
Definition: The code specifying the type of this product security tag.

DEN: Product_ Security Tag. Location. Code
Definition: The code specifying the location of this product security tag.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Details
Definition: An agreement between two or more parties, especially one that is written or spoken and enforceable by law and whose progress is monitored on a regular basis.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Fixed Fee_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the fixed fee that is to be awarded to the provider of goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract.
Usage Rule(s): In the case of fixed price contracts.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Non Fee Bearing_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the non fee bearing cost of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Completion. Percent
Definition: The percent of completion of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Type. Code
Definition: A code specifying the type of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Funding_ Type. Code
Definition: The code specifying the funding type, such as fixed price or a time and materials based, of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Security_ Type. Code
Definition: The code specifying the security type, such as commercial sensitivity or national security, of this progress monitored contract.
Usage Rule(s): It could indicate commercial sensitivity or national security.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Name. Text
Definition: The name, expressed as text, for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Description. Text
Definition: The textual description of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Issue. Date Time
Definition: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the issuance of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of a price for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Target_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the target price of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Estimated Total_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the estimated total price of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Initial Funding Target_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the initial funding target price for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Adjusted Funding Target_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the sum of the initial funding target price plus any negotiated adjustments to this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Ceiling_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the maximum price for this progress monitored contract taking into account only work that is fully scoped.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Estimated Ceiling_ Price. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the maximum estimated price for this progress monitored contract taking into account all in scope and out of scope work.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Extension. Indicator
Definition: The indication of whether or not this progress monitored contract can be or has been extended.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Start. Date
Definition: The date on which this progress monitored contract starts.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Work_ Start. Date
Definition: The date on which work specified in this progress monitored contract starts.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Definitization_ Start. Date
Definition: The date of the start of the definitization (final determination of an agreement, arrangement, or contract, such as about its cost, duration, scope, and/or go no-go decision) of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Target_ Fee. Percent
Definition: The percent value of the overall contract price to be granted as a fee to the provider of the goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Expected_ End. Date
Definition: The date of the expected end of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Estimated_ End. Date
Definition: The date of the estimated end of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Planned_ End. Date
Definition: The date of the planned end of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Last Item Delivery. Date
Definition: The date on which the last delivery of an item under this progress monitored contract has or will take place.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Over Target Baseline. Date
Definition: The date on which this progress monitored contract was re-scoped after exceeding the target baseline.
Usage Rule(s): Over target baseline is re-scoped when the target baseline has been exceeded due to an unrecoverable cost or schedule condition.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Original Negotiated_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the originally negotiated cost of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Target Fee_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the target fee that is to be awarded to the provider of the goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract if the negotiated cost of this contract is met.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Negotiated_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the negotiated cost of the goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract excluding any fee or profit to the provider of the goods or services.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Authorized Unpriced Work Estimated_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value that constitutes the estimate of the cost of work within this progress monitored contract which has been authorized, but the price of which has not been fully negotiated.
Short Name: Authorized Unpriced Work Estimated Cost Amount

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Cumulative Negotiated Changes_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value that constitutes the cumulative cost of contract changes that have occurred since the beginning of this progress monitored contract, excluding fee or profit.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Minimum Award Fee_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the minimum fee that can be awarded to the provider of goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract.
Usage Rule(s): In the case of incentive based contracts.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Maximum Award Fee_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the maximum fee that can be awarded to the provider of goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract.
Usage Rule(s): In the case of incentive based contracts.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Original Award Fee_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the fee that was originally awarded to the provider of the goods or services specified in this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Current Target_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the current target cost of this progress monitored contract, excluding fees or profit.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Total Allocated Budget_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the cost of the total budget allocated to this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Initial Funding Ceiling_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the cost of the initial funding ceiling for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Adjusted Funding Ceiling_ Cost. Amount
Definition: The monetary value of the cost of the funding ceiling including adjustments to this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Fiscal_ Funding Year. Date Time
Definition: A unique identifier of a fiscal year of funding for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Customer_ Name. Text
Definition: The customer name, expressed as text, for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Plan_ Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique plan identification for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Validity. Project_ Period
Definition: A period within which this progress monitored contract is a valid legal instrument.
Usage Rule(s): A contract is a valid legal instrument.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Identified. Contractor_ Party
Definition: A contractor party that is identified for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Identified. Appropriating_ Party
Definition: The appropriating party identified for this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Reference. Project_ Document
Definition: A project document referenced by this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Funds Authorization_ Reference. Project_ Document
Definition: The project document that details the authorization to fund this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Appropriation_ Effective. Project_ Period
Definition: The project period within which the appropriations for this progress monitored contract are, or will be, effective.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Effective. Project_ Period
Definition: A project period within which this progress monitored contract is, or will be, effective.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Modification. Awarded_ Contract Change
Definition: An awarded contract change describing modifications to the terms of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Associated. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost associated with this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Best Case Estimate At Completion_ Associated. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost that is a best case estimate at completion associated with this progress monitored contract.
Short Name: Best Case Estimate At Completion Cost

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Budget Baseline_ Associated. Project_ Cost
Definition: A budget baseline project cost associated with this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Most Likely Estimate At Completion_ Associated. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost that is a most likely estimate at completion associated with this progress monitored contract.
Short Name: Most Likely Estimate At Completion Cost

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Worst Case Estimate At Completion_ Associated. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost that is a worst case estimate at completion associated with this progress monitored contract.
Short Name: Worst Case Estimate At Completion Cost

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Principal. Specified_ Programme
Definition: The principal specified programme of this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Contained. Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio
Definition: A portfolio of individual projects contained within this progress monitored contract that are tracked together.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Incentive. Contract_ Performance Measurement
Definition: The contract performance measure which provides incentives for above expectations performance on this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Contained. Progress Monitored_ Project
Definition: A progress monitored project contained within this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Contract. Specified. Project_ Contract Line Item
Definition: A contract line item specified within this progress monitored contract.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Details
Definition: A collection of individual projects whose progress is monitored together.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier for this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Name. Text
Definition: The name, expressed as text, of this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Description. Text
Definition: The textual description of this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Category. Text
Definition: The category, expressed as text, for this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Component. Progress Monitored_ Project
Definition: A progress monitored project that comprises part of this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project Portfolio. Management Reserve. Project_ Cost
Definition: A management reserve set aside for contingencies that is accounted for as a project cost for this progress monitored project portfolio.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Details
Definition: An endeavour carefully planned and monitored to achieve a unique product, service, or other particular aim such as a construction project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Identification. Identifier
Definition: The unique identifier for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Contract. Identifier

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Project Portfolio. Identifier

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Description. Text

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Name. Text
Definition: The name, expressed as text, of this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Type. Code
Definition: The code specifying the type of progress monitored project, such as procurement or research and development.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Authority_ Constraint. Indicator

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Sub-Project_ Identification. Identifier
Definition: A unique sub-project identifier of this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Physical. Project_ Location
Definition: A physical project location for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Baseline_ Plan. Project_ Period
Definition: The baseline plan project period for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Actual_ Plan. Project_ Period
Definition: The actual plan project period for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Estimated_ Plan. Project_ Period
Definition: The estimated plan project period for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Reporting_ Plan. Project_ Period
Definition: The reporting plan project period for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Baseline. Project Schedule_ Calendar
Definition: A baseline project schedule calendar for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Baseline. Project Reporting_ Calendar

Definition: A management reserve set aside for contingencies that is accounted for as a project cost for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Undistributed Budget. Project_ Cost
Definition: An undistributed budget item representing project funds that has not been allocated to any task that is accounted for as a project cost for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Overhead. Project_ Cost
Definition: An overhead project cost representing the total of indirect costs required to complete a unit of work excluding general and administrative indirect costs for this progress monitored project.  For example, this includes labour and material overhead costs that are specific to the project and are independent of general and administrative overhead costs that are prorated across a pool of projects.

Definition: A project cost of funds borrowed to finance this progress monitored project.

Definition: An overhead project cost representing the portion of the indirect costs specifically related to the direction, control, and administration of a company or other entity for this progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Performance Measurement Baseline_ Total. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost representing the sum of all direct, indirect, funds borrowed, and undistributed budget costs allocated to perform work for the progress monitored project.

DEN: Progress Monitored_ Project. Allocated Budget_ Total. Project_ Cost
Definition: A project cost representing the sum of the budget allocated to the performance measurement baseline and any management reserves for this progress monitored project.

DEN: SPS_ Consignment. Consignee Receipt. SPS_ Location

DEN: SPS_ Consignment. Carrier. SPS_ Party

DEN: SPS_ Consignment. Delivery. SPS_ Party

DEN: SPS_ Consignment. Utilized. SPS_ Transport Equipment

DEN: SPS_ Location. Details

Definition: A reference to an individual, a group, or a body having a role in Sanitary and Phytosanitary (SPS) measures.

Consignor
Consignee

Delivery (Place of Destination)
Carrier
